     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>VAMapsIG</h2><p>The official URL for this implementation guide is: </p><pre>http://va.gov/fhir/ImplementationGuide/va.maps</pre><div><p>This implementation guide is a FHIR IG rendering of the KBS Map Set from VA sources (primarily VistA) to FHIR. Where appropriate these maps conform to the us-core profiles.</p>\n</div></div>"
  ] ; # 
